{"title":"革命传统接过来","authors":["吕林清"],"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":12,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命传统接过来\t吕林清"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗把路开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌声多豪迈；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红彤彤袖章映山水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“长征”队伍好气派！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颗颗红心向北京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胸怀开阔志不衰！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏着风雷走天下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命传统接过来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪怕什么风霜雨雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪怕什么刀山火海！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胸中自有方向盘——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《毛主席语录》放光彩！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"豪情满腔颂太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"处处是宣传的舞台；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到群众中滚一身泥土呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在斗争的风浪中长成材！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去熟悉社会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"熟悉群众，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把革命“真经”取回来；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜看前程多锦绣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红色江山春常在！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗把路开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌声多豪迈；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席栽培的小树苗呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做共产主义大厦的栋梁材！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}